title: Website Deployed - 23rd Febuary, 2024
content: I am excited to deploy the first version of this website!
With only a few more levels left to complete, a lot of effort is being put into creating this website as well as setting up the socials in preparation for the release of 'Galactic Dash'!
We now currently have a YouTube channel, Instagram and a new Discord server ready to go, with a subreddit and other socials on the way, ready for the next chapter of this journey.
A lot of work is being put in to get the Beta released by some time next week, I look forward to finally sharing this project with you all, hope you enjoy it!
